originalText.text:
I have been their patient for over 10 years and can not speak highly enough. They are always very thorough, professional and courteous. Appointments are always on time, the practice is sparkling clean and they will always try to accommodate if you have to change your appointment. They work seamlessly with my insurance providers that changed over the years and never had any billing issues, etc.

Dr. Senay has done multiple different procedures and never had any issues afterwards. He is always very clear and professional when explaining the finding as well as what needs to be done then or in the future. They keep a great record of examinations as well as x-rays with meticulous follow up on every appointment.

Highly recommend their hygienist as well!
